# Deployment and Infrastructure Guidelines

## Environment Configuration
1. Implement flavor system for:
   - Development
   - Staging
   - Production
2. Maintain separate configuration files per environment
3. Use environment variables for sensitive data
4. Implement proper API versioning

## CI/CD Pipeline
1. Required checks:
   - Static code analysis
   - Unit tests
   - Widget tests
   - Integration tests
   - Code coverage
2. Automated versioning
3. Build optimization
4. Release management

## Monitoring and Analytics
1. Integrate crash reporting (Firebase Crashlytics)
2. Implement analytics tracking
3. Monitor app performance
4. Track user engagement metrics

## Security
1. Secure storage for sensitive data
2. API security measures
3. Code obfuscation in release builds
4. Regular security audits

## Version Control
1. Follow semantic versioning
2. Maintain changelog
3. Document breaking changes
4. Ensure backward compatibility

## Documentation
1. Maintain up-to-date API documentation
2. Document build and deployment processes
3. Keep README files current
4. Document environment setup
